N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1242.1 - Dockage, definition of

State Regulations

The charge assessed against a vessel for berthing at a
wharf, pier, bulkhead structure, or bank, or for mooring to a vessel so
berthed. Notes
